109
00:08:34,620 --> 00:08:36,100
What's wrong then?

110
00:08:36,100 --> 00:08:39,520
Don't you think the experiment is a little slow?

111
00:08:39,520 --> 00:08:41,220
Slow?

112
00:08:43,020 --> 00:08:48,760
We're working on experiments with cell models and animal models at the same time for cross-control verification.

113
00:08:48,760 --> 00:08:53,860
The efficiency and rigor of experimental design have been greatly improved.

114
00:08:53,860 --> 00:08:55,820
It's already fast.

115
00:08:55,820 --> 00:08:57,620
Yes.

116
00:08:57,620 --> 00:08:59,620
I thought it was okay, too.

117
00:08:59,620 --> 00:09:03,600
