I clean the lab every day.

128
00:10:27,280 --> 00:10:29,580
What is the problem?

129
00:10:30,940 --> 00:10:33,340
The six plates of cells are all contaminated.

130
00:10:33,340 --> 00:10:35,080
Don't worry.

131
