156
00:13:19,100 --> 00:13:23,540
No. You got a fever. I'll get some medicine.

157
00:13:24,420 --> 00:13:27,680
It's late at night. It's not safe for you to go out alone.

158
00:13:27,680 --> 00:13:30,576
