159
00:13:30,576 --> 00:13:33,140
- Don't worry. 
 - You still have the nerve to mention that?

160
00:13:33,140 --> 00:13:37,020
When you were in Lakaya, you got a hole in your stomach.

161
00:13:39,200 --> 00:13:42,220
All right. Have a rest and stop talking.

162
00:13:55,400 --> 00:13:57,900
This is the only thing in the fridge.

163
00:13:59,020 --> 00:14:01,100
Bear with it.

164
00:14:04,200 --> 00:14:05,860
I feel better.

165
00:14:05,860 --> 00:14:08,700
That's good. Go to sleep.

166
00:14:08,700 --> 00:14:11,240
Get some sleep, and it will be fine tomorrow morning.

167
00:14:11,240 --> 00:14:12,960
Wei'an.

