188
00:16:16,580 --> 00:16:18,480
- Is that all right? 
 - Yes.

189
00:16:21,300 --> 00:16:24,660
I know my education is not high enough. I am not rich in experience, either.

190
00:16:24,660 --> 00:16:27,600
But for the basic operation, I can still finish it.

191
00:16:27,600 --> 00:16:29,700
Now I'm going to clean up the lab.

192
00:16:29,700 --> 00:16:34,560
If you trust me, I can help you clean your experimental vessels.

193
