Is anyone here?

200
00:18:14,340 --> 00:18:16,560
I am locked here.

201
00:18:22,860 --> 00:18:25,700
 Are you working overtime again?

202
00:18:25,700 --> 00:18:29,021
 You have the nerve to criticize me.

203
00:18:29,021 --> 00:18:31,620
 Why are you so hard on yourself?

204
00:18:31,620 --> 00:18:34,420
 You are so diligent.

205
00:18:34,420 --> 00:18:35,680

